  "detailed_description": "Gods decide to bring the flood of water upon the earth. <br>Salvage what you think is valuable and bring it back to base. <br>It's a psychological test in the apocalypse, and an interactive experiment in making choices.<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>More than 17 achievements & endings</strong></li></ul>Over 17 alternate endings and Easter eggs are waiting to be dug out.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/80c60a25915a59918fffa3fa452690a3.poster.avif?t=1770427252\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/80c60a25915a59918fffa3fa452690a3.webm?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/80c60a25915a59918fffa3fa452690a3.mp4?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Interactive puzzle visual novel</strong></li></ul>Various alternate scenes and props interaction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/8bb50fa40b8fb329a53513ffd98ed0ad.poster.avif?t=1770427252\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/8bb50fa40b8fb329a53513ffd98ed0ad.webm?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/8bb50fa40b8fb329a53513ffd98ed0ad.mp4?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A long mental journey</strong></li></ul>Every survivor will shape their own doomsday story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/7377e0cba3715734be9bed5ca00e5d77.poster.avif?t=1770427252\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/7377e0cba3715734be9bed5ca00e5d77.webm?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/7377e0cba3715734be9bed5ca00e5d77.mp4?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Doomsday's artistic metaphor</strong></li></ul>Every end of the journey is a reflection on humanity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/6dadcdd6c32b0c59d77a72ba25cd2737.poster.avif?t=1770427252\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/6dadcdd6c32b0c59d77a72ba25cd2737.webm?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411380/extras/6dadcdd6c32b0c59d77a72ba25cd2737.mp4?t=1770427252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
